<item>
            <title>[VFS-189] Possible NPE in DefaultFileSystemManager</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/VFS-189</link>
                <project id="12310495" key="VFS">Commons VFS</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;resolveName(FileName base, String, NameScope) does not protect from a null base variable and will lead to an exception on realBase.getPath() later on in the code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Fortify&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
